Wolfblade:

She grinned and let her optics close. In a soft, yet seductive 
tone, "Of course."
She wanted to stay in his arms, but duty called. Her honor codes 
wouldn't let pleasure get in the way of duty. Well, for the most 
part. Still in his arms, "SO what's the mission we have to go on? 
Something dangerous I hope?"
